snippet.title: BANANA BAJJI | Banana Fry | Valakkai Bajji Recipe  Cooking in Village | Tasty Plantain Evening Snack
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we made a delicious and crispy Banana Bajji using raw plantains, also known as Valakkai Bajji in Tamil. This traditional South Indian snack, especially in Kerala and Tamil Nadu, is a perfect evening treat, especially when served hot with tea. We sliced fresh plantains, dipped them in a flavorful gram flour batter seasoned with spices, and deep-fried them over a woodfire stove until golden and crisp.

Our village-style cooking brings out the authentic taste and aroma of this simple yet tasty snack. Watch how we prepare these bajjis in a natural outdoor setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional methods.

Enjoy the satisfying crunch and soft banana filling in every bite! Perfect for family gatherings or as a festive snack.
tags: how to make banana bajji at home

it.title: BAJI DI BANANE | Frittura di banane | Ricetta Valakkai Bajji Cucinare nel villaggio | Delizioso s...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo preparato un delizioso e croccante Banana Bajji usando platani crudi, noto anche come Valakkai Bajji in Tamil. Questo spuntino tradizionale dell'India meridionale, in particolare del Kerala e del Tamil Nadu, Ã¨ una delizia perfetta per la sera, soprattutto se servito caldo con il tÃ¨. Abbiamo affettato platani freschi, li abbiamo immersi in una saporita pastella di farina di ceci condita con spezie e li abbiamo fritti su una stufa a legna fino a quando non sono diventati dorati e croccanti.

La nostra cucina in stile villaggio esalta il gusto e l'aroma autentici di questo spuntino semplice ma gustoso. Guarda come prepariamo questi bajji in un ambiente naturale all'aperto, utilizzando ingredienti freschi e metodi tradizionali.

Gusta la croccantezza appagante e il morbido ripieno di banana in ogni boccone! Perfetto per le riunioni di famiglia o come spuntino festivo.

id.title: PISANG BAJI | Gorengan Pisang | Resep Masakan Valakkai Bajji di Desa | Camilan Lezat Malam Hari d...
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami membuat Bajji Pisang yang lezat dan renyah menggunakan pisang mentah, yang juga dikenal sebagai Valakkai Bajji dalam bahasa Tamil. Camilan tradisional India Selatan ini, khususnya di Kerala dan Tamil Nadu, merupakan sajian malam yang sempurna, terutama jika disajikan hangat dengan teh. Kami mengiris pisang segar, mencelupkannya ke dalam adonan tepung gram yang beraroma dan dibumbui dengan rempah-rempah, dan menggorengnya di atas tungku kayu bakar hingga berwarna keemasan dan renyah.

Cara memasak ala desa kami menghasilkan rasa dan aroma asli dari camilan sederhana namun lezat ini. Saksikan cara kami menyiapkan bajji ini di alam terbuka, menggunakan bahan-bahan segar dan metode tradisional.

Nikmati kerenyahan yang memuaskan dan isian pisang yang lembut di setiap gigitan! Sempurna untuk acara kumpul keluarga atau sebagai camilan hari raya.

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every game must come to an end.
Squid Game. The final season. June 27.
Only on Netflix.

More info on Squid Game Season 3:
A failed rebellion, the death of a friend, and a secret betrayal. Picking up in the aftermath of Season 2â€™s bloody cliffhanger, the third and final season of Netflixâ€™s most popular series finds Gi-hun, a.k.a. Player 456, at his lowest point yet. But the Squid Game stops for no one, so Gi-hun will be forced to make some important choices in the face of overwhelming despair as he and the surviving players are thrust into deadlier games that test everyoneâ€™s resolve. With each round, their choices lead to increasingly grave consequences. Meanwhile, In-ho resumes his role as Front Man to welcome the mysterious VIPs, and his brother Jun-ho continues his search for the elusive island, unaware thereâ€™s a traitor in their midst. Will Gi-hun make the right decisions, or will Front Man finally break his spirit?
Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime EmmysÂ®, becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Season 3 stars Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Wi Ha-jun, Park Gyu-young, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Jo Yu-ri, Chae Kuk-hee, Lee David, Roh Jae-won, and Jun Suk-ho, with special appearance by Park Hee-soon.

#TUDUM

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81615967

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Devastated after losing his friend, Player 456 presses on â€” challenging the Front Man's scheme in the final season of the globally most-watched series.

snippet.description:
Welcome to Women Ki Duniya â€” a hilarious sketch that flips the script on gender roles! ğŸ¤¯
What if women were the dominant gender in society? In this fun, satirical world, men are the ones being told to â€œsmile more,â€ struggling to get promoted, and balancing office work and house chores â€” while women run the show with power, sass, and zero tolerance for mansplaining. ğŸ˜ğŸ’…
From office meetings to family functions, this sketch hilariously reimagines everyday situations with the gender dynamics reversed, making you laugh and think at the same time!
Watch now and enter a world where patriarchy gets a taste of its own medicine! ğŸ’¥

snippet.title: Indians And Summer Season | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hello guys
This Video has all the things that happen in Indians And Summer Season . 

To buy Himalaya SunProtect+ here is the link of  - https://amzn.to/4iRtiwe

Every Indian in summer vacations going on vacation with family to hill stations like shimla , manali , mussoorie , darjeeling , haridwar , Rishikesh . Indian Aunties going on vacation on their girls trip to south inida exploring Karnataka , loving Bangalore monsoon weather , south indian food of mysore , dosa , idli , vada , appum  , shopping in local markets for their kids and missing them . Childhood memories of eating icecream kulfi , playing with street dogs , Garmi and light jana , mosquitoes in summers and fav ac wala room , electricity bill rising because of ac , mom obsessed with bijli ka bill , Cousins and their night stay at mosi house enjoying mango shake , playing uno cards , discussing horror ghost stories , bhoot ki baaten and creating memories , Swimming class sessions in summers , playing in swimming sessions . Trip with College friends and school friends , exploring the hotel room , collecting toiletries to take back home , clicking photos and alot of gossip . Kaamwali bai asking for vacation Dilli ki sadi garmi , putting up mini swimming pool for the kids in home cause Delhi summers are dry . Indian moms dealing with holiday homework given by school teachers during summer break , Family trips , horse ridding , trekking , hiking . watching sunsets , sunrise at famous hill tops , creating memories clicking pictures , tourist locations and rush of people and traffic jams , mother excited to go vacation getting her beauty regime by parlour didi , waxing , facial , threading , bleach , dtan , shopping from sarojini nagar to travel , buying gifts for relatives on vacay , travelling by train enjoying , singing eating train food , road trip with family , stopping at dhaba , mom feeding her home cooked food puri aloo jeera sabzi , middle class dad driving on highway , kids singing fighting taking pictures on the way to Himachal and so much more ..
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 

Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part,

Bhide is seeing at the cheque collection for the society maintenance and sees that Jetha's cheque is missing. He decides to go to Jetha's house to ask for it. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Dark Days Are Upon Us | Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
In a city without Heroes, Villains rise! Barbaric henchmen, crooked cops, and greedy Goblins lurk around every corner in our Dark Days Season. When Elixir is banned, a cohort of stylish, yet sinister Heroes will clash for infamy! Explore the Dark Days Scenery and transform your Village into a crooked cityscape that's truly a mischief maker's paradise. Meet some shady characters as you take on unique challenges and positively wicked Events!



Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter â–º https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-Â­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

In a city without Heroes, Villains rise! Barbaric henchmen, crooked cops, and greedy Goblins lurk around every corner in our Dark Days Season. When Elixir is banned, a cohort of stylish, yet sinister Heroes will clash for infamy! Explore the Dark Days Scenery and transform your Village into a crooked cityscape that's truly a mischief maker's paradise. Meet some shady characters as you take on unique challenges and positively wicked Events!



Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter â–º https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-Â­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Yeh Kahaani Ap Sab Ki - Gyan Gaming | Teaser
snippet.description:
Notes : Iâ€™ve been playing Free Fire since 2017 â€“ thatâ€™s seven years of dedication, passion, and countless memories and also I am the Oldest free fire Indian YouTuber till now . But over time, especially since 2021, Iâ€™ve witnessed something deeply disappointing: the gradual decline of the game I once loved, particularly on the Indian server.

Let me be clear â€” updates are meant to enhance a game, not break it. Sadly, it feels like each new update is pushing Free Fire further away from what made it special. And the reason? In my view, itâ€™s the poor handling by the current Free Fire India moderation team.

Instead of focusing on what the community truly wants, these moderators seem more interested in their own agendas. Creativity, innovation, and a deep understanding of gaming culture â€” these are essential traits for any successful game development team. Unfortunately, the current staff appears to lack all three.

Back in 2021, Free Fire was thriving. The gameplay, events, and community engagement were all on point. But today? Unbalanced updates, pay-to-win elements, a lack of genuine player feedback integration, and overall mismanagement have caused a steep decline.
I also think that free fire partner program is most corrupted . Free fire partner YouTubers are act like a slave . Even if the game is dead, they will say nothing . They are just happy with the salary and stuffs you provided them . They donâ€™t even think about the game . They donâ€™t talk where need to improve. They just clowns .

As a lifelong gamer whoâ€™s experienced countless titles across all platforms, I know what makes a game engaging and sustainable. And right now, Free Fire India is heading in the wrong direction.

In my upcoming video, Iâ€™ll be breaking down exactly how the game is being ruined, point by point, and what can be done to fix it. Itâ€™s time we speak up â€“ not because we hate the game, but because we love it and want to see it thrive again.

Garena, if you truly care about the future of Free Fire in India, itâ€™s time to replace the current moderators with a team that listens, creates,Â andÂ cares.

snippet.title: 3 Minecraft Speedrunners VS Herobrine
snippet.description:
We coded Herobrine into Minecraft, can we survive him, and beat Minecraft?

Patreon (Plugin): https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

Follow my socials:
â½ Twitter - @dream
â½ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
â½ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Merch: https://www.dream.shop

GeorgeNotFound: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 

We decided to take on Herobrine in Minecraft Manhunt! This video is a different rendition of normal Manhunt, where we go up against an AI bot that has abilities like the legend of Herobrine!

Herobrine has and probably always will be Minecraft's greatest evil villain. If Steve is Minecraft's best friend, Herobrine is it's enemy.

This was super challenging, but was a lot of fun. We made a video a while ago where we took on a terminator, and this is similar to that, but even more advanced and with special abilities!

Baritone: https://github.com/cabaletta/baritone

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.16 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my friend AND my friend AND my friend tries to prevent me from doing it. It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

If this video gets 1,000,000 likes we'll do a rematch!

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt

snippet.description:
Telusu Kada Release Date Announcement | Official Video 
#TelusuKada The much awaited Telugu romantic drama starring 
Siddhu Jonnalagadda, Raashii Khanna, and Srinidhi Shetty is 
finally here!  
Directed by debutant Neeraja Kona, this film explores the 
nuances of relationships, selflove, and sacrifice in a story that 
feels refreshingly original, emotionally layered, and thoroughly 
entertaining. 
With chart topping music by Thaman S, vibrant visuals, and a 
talented cast, Telusu Kada is set to be the perfect wholesome 
entertainer for the festive season. 
Mark your calendars for October 17, 2025 just ahead of Diwali 
and get ready for a cinematic celebration like no other!

snippet.title: Black Phone 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The phone is ringing again. Following the blockbuster success of Blumhouseâ€™s 2022 horror phenomenon, which earned more than $160 million worldwide and global critical acclaim, Universal Pictures announces the launch of a sinister new franchise with the release of Black Phone 2.

Ethan Hawke, Mason Thames, Madeleine McGraw, Jeremy Davies and Miguel Mora return for the filmâ€™s sequel, that will be directed by Scott Derrickson and is written by C. Robert Cargill and Derrickson.

The film will be produced by Jason Blum for Blumhouse, Scott Derrickson & C. Robert Cargill. Joe Hill and Ryan Turek are executive producer. Universal and Blumhouse will present the Crooked Highway Production.

Genre: Horror
Cast: Ethan Hawke, Mason Thames, Madeleine McGraw, Jeremy Davies, Miguel Mora
Director: Scott Derrickson
Written by: C. Robert Cargill, Scott Derrickson
Producers: Jason Blum, Scott Derrickson, C. Robert Cargill

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

--------------------------------------------------------
A regular morning turns tense for Jethalal when Babita reports a shocking incident involving one of his products. With multiple customers echoing the same concern, Jethalal must act fast to uncover the truth.

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #à¤¤à¤¾à¤°à¤•à¤®à¥‡à¤¹à¤¤à¤¾à¤•à¤¾à¤‰à¤²à¥à¤Ÿà¤¾à¤šà¤¶à¥à¤®à¤¾ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Step into Jethalalâ€™s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun.

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Reem Shaikh: Childhood, Career & Chaos
snippet.description:
Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Hardik Swagat Hai! 

Aaj ke khaas episode mein humare saath hain talented actress Reem Shaikh, jo choti si umar mein apna acting career shuru karke sabke dilon mein chhaa gayi hain. Reem khulkar baat karti hain apne career ki shuruaat ke baare mein, aur kaise unka safar Colors TV ke saath juda raha.

Woh batati hain apne latest show Laughter Chef ke mazedaar experiences aur apne pariwar ke liye unka pyar aur apni maa ke saath apne gehre rishte ke baare mein. Reem apne old-school nature aur emotional side ko bhi share karti hain, jo unhe alag banata hai.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
